\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 How many rooms were there in the house of Francis Street where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Oh it were only a little house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 A terrace?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 A little house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Do you remember how many rooms there were in it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 And - there were only me and me sister. Oh, me sister was lame. And - I had to take her to school, you see, so - when 
we - when we got to school - she went in at one door and I had to go in at the other do you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Do you remember how many rooms in the house where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 There were only two up and two down like - like -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 You and your sister slept in the back room and your mum and dad in the front?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Aye but we - we had a partition.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Across the middle of the room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 We had a partition - put across the middle of the room - you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Do you remember what your father did for a living?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 He was a collier.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Was he always a collier?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 He were always a collier. He were working when he were eight year old at pit. Eight year old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Did he tell you anything about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Well he - he said as - it were hard work getting up. He said, he said, it weren't a knocker up as he wanted, it were a puller out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 What did he do down the pit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 What did he do? He was a collier getting coal. Up the coal face. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Do you know where he was born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 He was born in Aspall.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Where's that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Aspall's in Wigan.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Where was your mother born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 And he buried his first wife from there and he lived in some housed they called stocking houses at Aspall.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Why stocking houses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Well it - they just named it the stocking houses. At Aspall. Again fingerpost. And he buried his first wife -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 That wasn't your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 
No. He buried his first wife at Heyes church and when me dad died I wanted to get that grave so I applied at Heyes but they said I couldn't have it, he said, the lynch}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8938406\charrsid15163457 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 gate had been built over top of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 So you couldn't have the grave?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 I couldn't have the grave. So -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Where did your mother come from? You don't remember where she came from - was he a Lancashire woman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 No. Me - me father - buried his first wife and then he }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4872671 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457  her - her sister. That was me mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 You don't remember where she came from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 I don't remember where they came - from.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Did your mother work at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Only doing washing for people you know, she used to take washing in for people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Tell me about it - how much she c}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8938406\charrsid15163457 h}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 arged, how much she got?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 
Well I'd - me dad said, you don't want do that sort of work. Her said, well, her said, it passes me time over. Well, he says, what do you gain by 
it? Say you do a bale of washing like that for half a crown - says it's not worth it. He says, you might as well sit in't chair. But she says - she liked doing it, it passed her time away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Did she have a job before she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4872671 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457  do you know and what was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 I don't know she - her younger days. Couldn't say that. The only thing - the only thing about it is - they used to go ride on some pon}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8938406\charrsid15163457 y}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457  - on some donkey's as were in a field you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Your mother and father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Me mother had. She use
d to go ride on these here donkeys you know - a farmer, he had a few donkeys and they used to go and tie some then they'd get on their backs and ride you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 This was in Westhoughton or when she was a child you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 This were at Aspall when me - when we were living at Aspall me mother used to go and have a ride on those here donkeys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 
When you were living in this house at Francis Street did anybody else live with you, relatives or were there just the four of you lived there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Did your mother have any paid help in the home or did she do all the housework herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Oh she did all - housework herself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Did she do all her own washing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Did her washing and somebody else's as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Did your mother make all your clothes or mend then?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Well she used to mend them you know. But not - not making 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Do you remember where they were bought? Were they always new?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Well - they were bought in Wigan. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Do you remember if there was any special occasion when you got new clothes for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 We generally used to get 'em for Easter. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Did your dad ever repair your shoes?
