ct, everybody - the younger }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8938406\charrsid15163457 and}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 
 used to think theirself fine - fine, you know, going to Sunday school at church you know dressed up in a new - new rig-out you know. That's what they used to think - think about you see.
