\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 You don't remember where they were bought?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 No, me}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8938406\charrsid15163457  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 
dad used to make our own - he used to buy soles. You could get soles
 ready cut out and he used to make - make 'em out of some old shoes as we had. He cut - he cut 'em all off - and he'd fix these soles and nail 'em - put welting round you see, put iron on. That - that was saving - saving money do you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Did your fat
