\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Wasn't he in any clubs at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 
Anyway up - they sent one and he told him go away. Week after they sent another. And they were all waiting when me dad come home for work. And - me mother says, there's another fellow here on same errand as that other. Well that got me 
- me dad worked up you know. So he walks through into the back kitchen and puts his can and his tommy tin down on't table and he comes to this here fellow and this fellow had put his straw hat on sideboard you know. Summertime. He didn't let him speak, he
 got hold of him be - neck like this here, lifted him up off his chair like that, took him to door opened door and pushed him out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 So he didn't believe in clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 This - this poor man says, give me me hat - give me hat. He says I'll give you the hat. Threw it at him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 He broke the hat and threw it at him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 He says, if you send another boy I'll kill the next one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 He didn't have any clubs at all - boot clubs or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 No. Well - he wouldn't - he wouldn't have 'em coming unless me mother had got 'em do you see unknowings to him.
