\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 When you were young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Aye.
