 that's a rope pulling all full tubs up with coal in and one ropes pulling full ones up while the other's taking empties down, you see. There's full'ens coming up, empties going down - he used to work on that. And there used to be a chain round a rope for
 pulling the empties and he you to put your hand on that chain and stop it and unhook it but - drag tubs off.
