\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 It's - well they used to have meetings in the room and the}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6184924\charrsid15163457 
y used to be singing in - in th}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 at room - they used to sing in that room.
