.
 He says, how? I says, I'll show you. When he made - when he made some of these tablets I says, now, I says, that drum is marked a, the next drum's marked b, in alphabetical order. I says, now tell our engineer when he's getting them to take 'em in alphab
etical order - a first, b, c a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6710063\charrsid15163457 nd so on through - through th'al}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 phabet as many tins as there are do you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Did you like your job at Wigglesworth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 Yes. Just a - so - he - he must have told manager about this you knows. Never mind, in a week or two I got me notice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5600746 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 What excuse did they make?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4659335 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8394249\charrsid15163457 
